metadata.name: the MOON
metadata.description:
the MOON is my metaphor of youth, high hopes & aspirations.

It has always charmed me. Here are my thoughts about what is happening on the far side of the Moon. That's what I felt when I was a teen.
Hope you will look at it and it will take you back to your age of innocence, too.

I wish I managed to allegorise my feelings, thoughts and dreams. A little bit of modern art, a pinch of theatrical scenery and a handful of feminine beauty are combined to create this artwork.

It's not about nudity, it's about purity of mind.

This is my very first NFT on Foundation.
